OL,3,CGovernment urged to make nutrition
OL,4,Clabels on front of food packaging
OL,5,Cmandatory
OL,7,FNutrition labels on the front of food
OL,8,Fpackaging should be made mandatory in
OL,9,Fthe UK, according to a consumer
OL,10,Fchampion.
OL,12,FWhich? called on the Government to
OL,13,Fmake the change amid what it described
OL,14,Fas an "obesity crisis".
OL,16,FA "better approach" is needed to help
OL,17,Fpeople make healthier choices, it said.
