OL,3,CGovernment urged to make nutrition
OL,4,Clabels on front of food packaging
OL,5,Cmandatory
OL,7,FIt comes after research by the group
OL,8,Ffound shoppers prefer traffic light
OL,9,Flabelling, although they said it could
OL,10,Fbe improved with more prominent
OL,11,Fplacing and increased size.
OL,13,FTraffic light labelling on food
OL,14,Fpackaging was introduced in 2013 and
OL,15,Fuses green (low), amber (medium), and
OL,16,Fred (high) colours to show fat,
OL,17,Fsaturated fat, sugar, and salt
OL,18,Fcontent, plus calories.
