OL,4,Clabels on front of food packaging
OL,5,Cmandatory
OL,7,FThe system is not mandatory in the UK,
OL,8,Falthough it is voluntarily used by
OL,9,Fmajor manufacturers and retailers.
OL,11,FHowever, according to Which? the
OL,12,Fsystem is used inconsistently.
OL,14,FIt claims some shops do not include
OL,15,Ftraffic light labelling, or provide it
OL,16,Fwithout colour coding.
