OL,3,CGovernment urged to make nutrition
OL,4,Clabels on front of food packaging
OL,5,Cmandatory
OL,7,FResearch by Which? captured insights
OL,8,Fthrough the mobile phones of more than
OL,9,F500 shoppers to find out how the
OL,10,Ftraffic light system is working for
OL,11,Fcustomers.
OL,13,FA third (33%) said that the nutrition
OL,14,Flabel was the first thing they looked
OL,15,Fat on the front of a pack.
OL,17,FPeople most used the traffic light
OL,18,Fsystem when choosing snacks (56%),
OL,19,Fdairy products (33%) and breakfast
OL,20,Fcereals (27%).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
