OL,5,Cmandatory
OL,7,FAlmost half (47%) said they found this
OL,8,Flabelling easy to understand.
OL,10,FIn focus groups, the traffic light
OL,11,Fsystem was the preferred food
OL,12,Flabelling option, although suggestions
OL,13,Fto improve it included making it more
OL,14,Fprominent and larger.
OL,16,FWhich? said that people also called
OL,17,Ffor making the scheme easier to
OL,18,Funderstand, such as making the
OL,19,Frecommended serving size on some
OL,20,Fproducts more realistic and consistent.
