OL,3,CGovernment urged to make nutrition
OL,4,Clabels on front of food packaging
OL,5,Cmandatory
OL,7,FThe consumer champion is now calling
OL,8,Fon the Government to introduce a
OL,9,Fmandatory front-of-pack nutrition
OL,10,Flabelling scheme.
OL,12,FIt said this could build on the
OL,13,Fexisting traffic light system to make
OL,14,Fit work better for shoppers by
OL,15,Fbolstering consistency, making it more
OL,16,Fprominent and removing aspects people
OL,17,Fmay find confusing.
