OL,3,CGovernment urged to make nutrition
OL,4,Clabels on front of food packaging
OL,5,Cmandatory
OL,7,FSue Davies, head of food policy at
OL,8,FWhich?, said: "The UK is in the midst
OL,9,Fof an obesity crisis and it's clear
OL,10,Fthat a better approach to front-of-
OL,11,Fpack labelling is needed to help
OL,12,Fshoppers make healthier choices.
OL,14,F"Which? is calling on the Government
OL,15,Fto ensure that all manufacturers and
OL,16,Fretailers use front of pack nutrition
OL,17,Flabelling, ideally by making this
OL,18,Fmandatory.
