OL,3,CGovernment urged to make nutrition
OL,4,Clabels on front of food packaging
OL,5,Cmandatory
OL,7,F"Our research shows that people still
OL,8,Fprefer traffic light nutrition
OL,9,Flabelling, but that the current scheme
OL,10,Fneeds updating so that it is clearer
OL,11,Fand simpler and works better for
OL,12,Fconsumers.
OL,14,F"The new system should be backed up
OL,15,Fwith effective enforcement and
OL,16,Foversight by the Food Standards Agency
OL,17,Fand Food Standards Scotland, so
OL,18,Fshoppers have full trust in the labels
OL,19,Fon their food."
