OL,7,FIn 2022, some 64% of adults in England
OL,8,Fwere estimated to be overweight or
OL,9,Fliving with obesity.
OL,11,FIn November it also emerged that one
OL,12,Fin 10 children in the first year of
OL,13,Fprimary school in England is obese,
OL,14,Fthe highest figure on record outside
OL,15,Fthe pandemic.
OL,17,FIt is estimated that obesity costs the
OL,18,FNHS more than #11 billion every year.
