OL,7,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "This Government is
OL,9,Fbringing in a modernised food nutrient
OL,10,Fscoring system to reduce obesity.
OL,12,F"It's just one element of the strong
OL,13,Faction we are taking to tackle the
OL,14,Fobesity crisis as part of our 10 Year
OL,15,FHealth Plan, which will shift the
OL,16,Ffocus from sickness to prevention.
